snippet.title: TIME'S UP for Hollywood?! Celebrity Charity Accused of LAVISH Spending Spree!
snippet.description:
Hollywood backed non-profit Time's Up is accused of raising over $3.6 million dollars to help lessen harassment in Hollywood, only to spend a FRACTION of the money raised on actual victims of harassment. Instead they spend an exorbitant amount of money on salaries and celebrity getaways. Time's Up celebrity board includes Reese Witherspoon, Amy Schumer and Brie Larson. Uh oh!
